{{hstr|996}}
בּין / bêyn / bane
=== Etymology ===

(Sometimes in the plural masculine or feminine); properly the constructively contracted form of an otherwise unused noun from H995; 
=== Preposition ===
a distinction; but used only as a preposition, [[between]] (repeated before each noun, often with other particles); also as a conjugation, either... or: - among, asunder, at, between (-twixt . . . and), + from (the widest), X in, out of, whether (it be... or), within.